    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在《秩序：新曙光》这款融合了太空冒险要素的经营模拟游戏中，化身传奇舰长，带领你的小队在沙漠行星“新泰拉”上开启自己的史诗故事。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >重建秩序</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >来自联合星系的传奇舰长，也就是您，在率领小队平定一场席卷了数个星系的叛乱时，意外来到“间隙原点”这片与世隔绝的星区。间隙原点内唯一的星际文明——泰拉王国，其母星已在两百年前的战争中毁灭，活下来的人们四散在星区各处，或苟且偷生，或落草为盗，或偏安一隅。</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >无缝延展的星系地图</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3080070/extras/62e0ef3d53cb1a98805d4a73bb464473.poster.avif?t=1769492927\" width=800 height=265 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3080070/extras/62e0ef3d53cb1a98805d4a73bb464473.webm?t=1769492927\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >探寻各异的太空设施</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3080070/extras/d31f651fff34b96dd27396fab1c9b887.poster.avif?t=1769492927\" width=800 height=264 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3080070/extras/d31f651fff34b96dd27396fab1c9b887.webm?t=1769492927\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3080070/extras/d31f651fff34b96dd27396fab1c9b887.mp4?t=1769492927\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>构建星际运输网络</strong></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3080070/extras/9ba4ac2e41d513331c008993e8a87679.poster.avif?t=1769492927\" width=800 height=264 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3080070/extras/9ba4ac2e41d513331c008993e8a87679.webm?t=1769492927\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3080070/extras/9ba4ac2e41d513331c008993e8a87679.mp4?t=1769492927\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >探索未知的星球</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3080070/extras/7da21f7175d3cad3d3a63beadf03fc38.poster.avif?t=1769492927\" width=800 height=264 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3080070/extras/7da21f7175d3cad3d3a63beadf03fc38.webm?t=1769492927\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3080070/extras/7da21f7175d3cad3d3a63beadf03fc38.mp4?t=1769492927\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >采集地表所有可用资源</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3080070/extras/0bba19003ac052bb7df64c0fc0099c65.poster.avif?t=1769492927\" width=800 height=264 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3080070/extras/0bba19003ac052bb7df64c0fc0099c65.webm?t=1769492927\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3080070/extras/0bba19003ac052bb7df64c0fc0099c65.mp4?t=1769492927\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >构筑殖民地的每一寸角落</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3080070/extras/93aaeabef7e9f62081c7646bd1f5c040.poster.avif?t=1769492927\" width=800 height=264 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3080070/extras/93aaeabef7e9f62081c7646bd1f5c040.webm?t=1769492927\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3080070/extras/93aaeabef7e9f62081c7646bd1f5c040.mp4?t=1769492927\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >面对这片太空废土，是选择重建秩序，或是任其沉沦，还是带来更大的混乱？</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >无论如何，联合星系的先进技术将是您前进的利剑。采集资源、解锁科技，建立您的基地，从规划房间，到组建太空舰队，再到修建行星、星系巨构，您的足迹将遍及沙漠、雪原、火山，旧王国的地面基地或太空设施，乃至某些被污染的生物巢穴……</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><u>看着眼熟？这样的场景，此时此刻正在银河各处上演！</u><strong>关注我们</strong>：</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >B站：秩序新曙光制作组</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >官方群：759143587</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
